Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:09.67,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an9\fs13}升起的太阳  通红的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:15.42,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an9\fs13}随风飘扬  勾画路线
